    <comment type="function">
      <text evidence="2">Sesquiterpene synthase converting farnesyl diphosphate into two major products, zingiberene > beta-sesquiphellandrene, and five minor products, 7-epi-sesquithujene, sesquisabinene A, (E)-alpha-bergamotene, (E)-beta-farnesene and beta-bisabolene. Can also accept geranyl diphosphate as substrate, producing nine monoterpenes, with myrcene, limonene and alpha-terpinolene as the major products.</text>
    </comment>
